title: NFL
description: Over his 17-year pro career, Lewis' statistics and accolades were mind-boggling: 12 Pro Bowls, 2-time Defensive Player of the Year, 2 Super Bowl titles with the Ravens, and he's the only player with over 40 sacks and 30 interceptions.
